### API Endpoints Available

| Method | Endpoint | Description |
|---|---|---|
| `GET` | `/` | Health check |
| `GET` | `/health` | Detailed health status |
| `GET` | `/api/sources/` | List all sources (filterable) |
| `POST` | `/api/sources/` | Add a new source |
| `PUT` | `/api/sources/{id}` | Update a source |
| `DELETE` | `/api/sources/{id}` | Delete a source |
| `GET` | `/api/runs/` | List run history |
| `POST` | `/api/runs/trigger` | Manually trigger a pipeline run |
| `GET` | `/api/findings/` | Browse findings (search, filter, paginate) |
| `GET` | `/api/findings/stats` | Finding statistics for dashboard |
| `GET` | `/api/digests/` | List digests |
| `GET` | `/api/digests/{id}/pdf` | Download digest PDF |

### Pre-Configured Sources (20 total)
- **6 Competitors**: OpenAI, Anthropic, Google DeepMind, Meta AI, Mistral, Cohere
- **4 Model Providers**: OpenAI Platform, Google AI Studio, Anthropic API, AWS Bedrock
- **5 Research**: arXiv CS.CL/CS.LG/CS.AI, Semantic Scholar, Papers With Code
- **5 Benchmarks**: Open LLM Leaderboard, HF Trending Models/Datasets, Chatbot Arena

## Verification Results

- ✅ Server starts on `http://127.0.0.1:8000`
- ✅ `GET /health` → `200 OK`
- ✅ `GET /api/sources/` → `200 OK` (20 pre-seeded sources)
- ✅ `POST /api/runs/trigger` → `202 Accepted`
- ✅ `GET /api/findings/stats` → `200 OK`
- ✅ Swagger docs available at `http://127.0.0.1:8000/docs`
- ✅ SQLite database created and populated automatically

## Next Steps

**Phase 2**: Core Pipeline Infrastructure — Fetcher, Extractor, Change Detector, Summarizer
